OL,3,CTrump says US 'better off' without
OL,4,CIran deal as troops to leave Germany
OL,6,FDonald Trump has questioned whether
OL,7,Fthe US would be "better off" without a
OL,8,Fdeal with Iran, after stating that he
OL,9,Fwas "not satisfied" with the nation's
OL,10,Fpeace proposal.
OL,12,FIran handed over its latest proposal
OL,13,Ffor negotiations with the US to
OL,14,Fmediators in Pakistan on Thursday
OL,15,Fnight, Iran's state-run IRNA news
OL,16,Fagency said.
OL,18,FThe US president told reporters he was
OL,19,F"not satisfied" with the proposed plan
OL,20,Fas he left the White House for Florida
OL,21,Fon Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
