OL,3,CTrump says US 'better off' without
OL,4,CIran deal as troops to leave Germany
OL,6,FSpeaking at an event at the Raymond F.
OL,7,FKravis Center, in West Palm Beach,
OL,8,FFlorida, Trump then questioned whether
OL,9,Fthe US should make a deal at all, as
OL,10,Fhe described the war as "going on too
OL,11,Flong".
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,F"Frankly, maybe we're better off not
OL,19,Fmaking a deal at all. Do you want to
OL,20,Fknow the truth? Because we can't let
OL,21,Fthis thing go on," Trump said.
