OL,3,CTrump says US 'better off' without
OL,4,CIran deal as troops to leave Germany
OL,6,FThe conflict reached its 60-day
OL,7,Fdeadline yesterday, meaning it
OL,8,Frequires congressional authorisation
OL,9,Fto continue under the War Powers
OL,10,Fresolution - but the Trump
OL,11,Fadministration claimed the law does
OL,12,Fnot apply due to the ongoing ceasefire
OL,13,Fbetween the countries.
OL,15,F"There has been no exchange of fire
OL,16,Fbetween the United States Forces and
OL,17,FIran since April 7, 2026. The
OL,18,Fhostilities that began on February 28,
OL,19,F2026 have terminated," Trump wrote to
OL,20,Fcongressional leaders on Friday. )
