OL,3,CTrump says US 'better off' without
OL,4,CIran deal as troops to leave Germany
OL,6,FThe countries have not exchanged fire
OL,7,Fsince April 7, when a ceasefire was
OL,8,Ffirst agreed for two weeks, before
OL,9,Flater being extended indefinitely.
OL,11,FBut the US has been engaged in a naval
OL,12,Fblockade of Iranian ports along the
OL,13,FStrait of Hormuz since April 13, in
OL,14,Fresponse to Iran almost entirely
OL,15,Fclosing the waterway to the rest of
OL,16,Fthe world.
OL,18,FUS to withdraw troops from Germany
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
