OL,3,CTrump says US 'better off' without
OL,4,CIran deal as troops to leave Germany
OL,6,FThe US is set to withdraw around 5,000
OL,7,Ftroops from Germany in the next six to
OL,8,F12 months, after the president clashed
OL,9,Fwith the German chancellor over the
OL,10,Fwar in Iran.
OL,12,FDonald Trump threatened to withdraw
OL,13,Ftroops earlier this week after
OL,14,FChancellor Friedrich Merz said the US
OL,15,Fwas being "humiliated" by Iran's
OL,16,Fleadership and criticised Washington's
OL,17,Flack of strategy in the war.
OL,26,@wD@KOUwD@VO]
