OL,3,CTrump says US 'better off' without
OL,4,CIran deal as troops to leave Germany
OL,6,FThe US has a significant military
OL,7,Fpresence in Germany, with more than
OL,8,F36,000 active duty troops assigned to
OL,9,Fbases across the country as of last
OL,10,FDecember.
OL,12,FThe number of troops leaving would be
OL,13,F14% of the 36,000 US service members
OL,14,Fstationed there.
OL,16,F"This decision follows a thorough
OL,17,Freview of the Department's force
OL,18,Fposture in Europe and is in
OL,19,Frecognition of theater requirements
OL,20,Fand conditions on the ground,"
OL,21,FPentagon spokesman Sean Parnell said.
