OL,3,CTrump says US 'better off' without
OL,4,CIran deal as troops to leave Germany
OL,6,FTrump has continually hit out at
OL,7,FEuropean allies for not doing more to
OL,8,Fassist the US-Israel war on Iran, and
OL,9,Fsaid on Wednesday he was thinking of
OL,10,Fremoving troops from countries that
OL,11,Fhad not been supportive enough.
OL,13,F"The United States is studying and
OL,14,Freviewing the possible reduction of
OL,15,Ftroops in Germany, with a
OL,16,Fdetermination to be made over the next
OL,17,Fshort period of time," Trump said on
OL,18,FTruth Social on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
