OL,3,CTrump says US 'better off' without
OL,4,CIran deal as troops to leave Germany
OL,6,FThe next day he then posted that Merz
OL,7,Fshould "spend more time on ending the
OL,8,Fwar with Russia/Ukraine" and "fixing
OL,9,Fhis broken Country" than concerning
OL,10,Fhimself with Iran.
OL,12,FGerman Defense Minister Boris
OL,13,FPistorius said on Saturday the US
OL,14,Fdecision to withdraw was "anticipated".
OL,16,F"If we are to remain transatlantic, we
OL,17,Fmust strengthen the European pillar
OL,18,Fwithin Nato," he said.
