OL,6,FAn airstrike on a car in the village
OL,7,Fof Kfar Dajal killed two people, while
OL,8,Fanother hit a home in the village of
OL,9,FLwaizeh killing three, according to
OL,10,FLebanon's state-run National News
OL,11,FAgency.
OL,13,FA strike on the village of Shoukin
OL,14,Falso killed two people, the agency
OL,15,Fsaid.
