OL,6,FIsrael's military Arabic-language
OL,7,Fspokeswoman, Lt. Col. Ella Waweya,
OL,8,Fposted on X that the Israeli air force
OL,9,Fcarried out about 50 airstrikes over
OL,10,Fthe past 24 hours, saying that they
OL,11,Ftargeted Hezbollah infrastructure and
OL,12,Fmembers.
OL,14,FHezbollah said that it attacked
OL,15,FIsraeli troops who gathered inside a
OL,16,Fhouse in the coastal village of Bayed
OL,17,Fwith a drone on Saturday.
